  "time_ut": 1657868914,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87.\u0ba4\u0bca.\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd:",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "EC Member Atakasam: Hitting the cylinders:",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Susai Alexander, a member of the Sri Lanka Workers' Congress (SLC) of the Norwood Regional Council, kicked and punched the cylinders placed in the fuel queue and warned a bystander. He also took out the bottle hidden in his waist and tried to stab him and lashed out with blasphemous words.",
        "In this case, the general secretary of ECJ Jeevan Thondaman has said that an investigation will be conducted against him and till then, he will be suspended from the party.",
        "\"The High Level Disciplinary Committee of the Sri Lankan Labor Congress will conduct appropriate investigations on the 21st (Thursday) regarding the controversies and accusations against Norwood Regional Council member Soosai Alexander.",
        "Jeevan Thondaman has said that the EC will never allow such activities and all party membership rights of the said Pradeshiya Sabha member have been temporarily suspended with effect."
      ],
